### Service Registry — Dashboard & Registration Endpoints
### All requests go directly to registry (port 3075) — not through gateway

### List all registered services (dashboard)
GET http://localhost:3075/v1/registry/services
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get instances of a specific service
GET http://localhost:3075/v1/registry/services/core-service
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Manually register a service
POST http://localhost:3075/v1/registry/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test-service",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "host": "localhost",
  "port": 9999
}

###

### Send heartbeat
PUT http://localhost:3075/v1/registry/heartbeat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test-service",
  "port": 9999
}

###

### Deregister a service
DELETE http://localhost:3075/v1/registry/deregister
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test-service",
  "port": 9999
}

###

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3075/health

###

### Readiness check
GET http://localhost:3075/ready

###

### Swagger docs
GET http://localhost:3075/docs
